       The paper size can be set in the _D_E_S_C file or with command-line options
       to  ggrroollbbpp.  If the paper size is specified both ways, the command-line
       options take precedence over  the  contents  of  the  _D_E_S_C  file  (this
       applies to the page orientation too).

       See ggrrooffff__ffoonntt(5) how to set the paper dimensions in the _D_E_S_C file.

       To set the paper size in the command line, add

