       or

         ----ppaappeerrssiizzee==_p_a_p_e_r_-_s_i_z_e

       to  the other ggrroollbbpp options, where _p_a_p_e_r_-_s_i_z_e is in the same format as
       in the _D_E_S_C file.

       If no paper size is specified in the _D_E_S_C file or the command  line,  a
       default size of A4 is used.

